{"word":"ἀμέριμνος","slug":"ἀμέριμνος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀμέριμνος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:μέριμνα'><el>μέριμνα</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>free from care, unconcerned</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <i>uncared for, unheeded</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>driving away care</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}